org.apache.paimon.format.parquet.reader

Class ParquetDecimalVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.paimon.format.parquet.reader.ParquetDecimalVector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BytesColumnVector, ColumnVector, DecimalColumnVector, IntColumnVector, LongColumnVector, WritableBytesVector, WritableColumnVector, WritableIntVector, WritableLongVector

    public class ParquetDecimalVector
extends Object
implements DecimalColumnVector, WritableLongVector, WritableIntVector, WritableBytesVector
    Parquet write decimal as int32 and int64 and binary, this class wrap the real vector to provide DecimalColumnVector interface.
